<h3>About this module</h3>

  <p>This module is a fork of <strong>CGSimpleSmarty</strong> developed by <strong>Robert Campbell &lt;calguy1000&gt;</strong>.<br />
      This is a 1st generation fork of the module. Consider this as another flavour of the original module.<br />

  If you find any bugs please feel free to submit a bug report <a href="http://dev.cmsmadesimple.org/bug/list/1463" target="_blank">here</a> or for any good ideas consider submiting a feature request <a href="http://dev.cmsmadesimple.org/feature_request/list/1463" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
  <p>Please keep in mind that developers do have their daily jobs which means that feature requests are considered and done as time allows. If you need a feature really badly consider contacting one of the developers for a sponsored development.
